Instructions
Create a function titled printEvenNums. This function should accept an array as an argument and console.log all even values from the array.

Answer Code

function printEvenNums(arr) {
    for (var i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
        if (arr[i] % 2 === 0) {
            console.log(arr[i]);
        }
    }
}
